382
00:28:22,049 --> 00:28:23,049
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau ingin kita semua mati?</font>

383
00:28:23,609 --> 00:28:24,979
<font color=#FFFF00>Haruskah kita mati kelaparan di sini?</font>

384
00:28:25,549 --> 00:28:27,609
<font color=#FFFF00>Sadarlah kalian ini!</font>

385
00:28:28,779 --> 00:28:30,679
<font color=#FFFF00>Yang menemukan sekoci ini aku.</font>

386
00:28:30,809 --> 00:28:32,509
