393
00:28:47,449 --> 00:28:48,649
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau itu tidak ingin hidup?</font>

394
00:28:50,179 --> 00:28:51,579
<font color=#FFFF00>Percuma kalau kita
bertahan hidup sendirian.</font>

395
00:28:53,549 --> 00:28:56,549
