398
00:29:04,579 --> 00:29:05,849
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika kalian ingin menyelamatkan mereka...,</font>

399
00:29:06,279 --> 00:29:08,379
<font color=#FFFF00>...berenang saja sana, atau
