400
00:29:08,379 --> 00:29:09,849
<font color=#FFFF00>Lepas!/
Hei!</font>

401
00:29:15,049 --> 00:29:18,379
<font color=#FFFF00>Brengsek kau.
Bisa-bisanya kau begitu egois?</font>

402
00:29:18,849 --> 00:29:20,149
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak menyangka
kalau kau itu sampah.</font>

403
00:29:20,249 --> 00:29:21,549
<font color=#FFFF00>Jaga ucapanmu. Aku ini seniormu.</font>

404
00:29:21,549 --> 00:29:23,979
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan bodohi dirimu sendiri./
Minggir!</font>

405
00:29:24,879 --> 00:29:26,109
<font color=#FFFF00>Hei.</font>

406
00:29:26,309 --> 00:29:27,979
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau sudah gila?!</font>

407
00:29:32,149 --> 00:29:34,279
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika kalian ingin hidup,
