408
00:29:35,049 --> 00:29:36,979
<font color=#FFFF00>Berhenti bertindak konyol!</font>

409
00:29:41,909 --> 00:29:43,579
<font color=#FFFF00>Akan kucegah orang ini.
Kalian pergilah!</font>

410
00:29:44,209 --> 00:29:45,749
<font color=#FFFF00>Satu, dua, tiga.</font>

411
00:29:51,879 --> 00:29:52,949
<font color=#FFFF00>Lepas!</font>

412
00:29:54,049 --> 00:29:56,609
<font color=#FFFF00>Satu, dua./
Satu, dua.</font>

413
00:29:57,609 --> 00:29:58,649
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak!</font>

414
00:30:00,249 --> 00:30:01,779
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika ada apa-apa yang
