415
00:30:03,209 --> 00:30:04,579
<font color=#FFFF00>...kau dan Choi Tae Ho...</font>

416
00:30:07,309 --> 00:30:08,549
<font color=#FFFF00>...aku takkan memaafkan kalian.</font>

417
00:30:09,379 --> 00:30:11,049
<font color=#FFFF00>Memang kau
bisa berbuat apa pada kami?</font>

418
00:30:13,549 --> 00:30:14,549
<font color=#FFFF00>Tunggu saja.</font>

419
00:30:16,079 --> 00:30:17,449
<font color=#FFFF00>Lihat saja apa yang bisa kulakukan.</font>

420
00:30:28,509 --> 00:30:30,509
<font color=#FFFF00>Brengsek.</font>

421
00:30:39,649 --> 00:30:40,809
<font color=#FFFF00>Brengsek!</font>

422
00:30:41,079 --> 00:30:42,849
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita ini harus bertahan hidup!</font>

423
00:30:45,809 --> 00:30:47,209
<font color=#FFFF00>Dasar brengsek kau!</font>

424
00:31:00,479 --> 00:31:02,209
<font color=#FFFF00>Mendayung sesuai aba-abaku!</font>

425
00:31:02,209 --> 00:31:03,949
<font color=#FFFF00>Ombaknya terlalu kuat./
Hitung bersamaku.</font>

426
00:31:03,949 --> 00:31:06,349
<font color=#FFFF00>Lakukan seperti ini. Satu.</font>

427
00:31:07,179 --> 00:31:08,409
<font color=#FFFF00>Dua./
Satu.</font>

428
00:31:09,079 --> 00:31:11,679
<font color=#FFFF00>Dua. Sekocinya jalan 'kan?/
Satu.</font>

429
00:31:11,879 --> 00:31:14,009
<font color=#FFFF00>Sepertinya.../
Teruskan.</font>

430
00:31:14,009 --> 00:31:15,049
<font color=#FFFF00>Dua!</font>

431
00:31:15,379 --> 00:31:17,179
<font color=#FFFF00>Satu, dua./
Satu, dua.</font>

432
00:31:17,179 --> 00:31:18,849
<font color=#FFFF00>Bukannya kita mundur sekarang?</font>

433
00:31:18,879 --> 00:31:21,209
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak, itu cuma perasaanmu saja./
