434
00:31:21,209 --> 00:31:22,249
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita bergerak maju.</font>

435
00:31:22,249 --> 00:31:24,979
<font color=#FFFF00>Tae Ho menarik sekocinya!/
Apa?</font>

436
00:31:24,979 --> 00:31:26,949
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita mundur./
Hei!</font>

437
00:31:27,079 --> 00:31:28,809
<font color=#FFFF00>Tae Ho!/
Kita harus menyelamatkan mereka!</font>

438
00:31:31,479 --> 00:31:32,549
<font color=#FFFF00>Hei!</font>

439
00:31:33,279 --> 00:31:35,279
<font color=#FFFF00>Brengsek! Dia menusuk sekocinya!</font>

440
00:31:37,579 --> 00:31:38,679
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau ombaknya sudah
mulai reda...,</font>

441
00:31:39,709 --> 00:31:41,349
<font color=#FFFF00>...kita akan memperbaiki
