442
00:31:42,449 --> 00:31:43,779
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika kalian ingin bertahan hidup...,</font>

443
00:31:45,109 --> 00:31:46,249
<font color=#FFFF00>...dengarkan apa kataku.</font>

444
00:31:51,179 --> 00:31:53,279
<font color=#FFFF00>Dasar bajingan gila kau!</font>

445
00:31:53,279 --> 00:31:56,709
<font color=#FFFF00>Tarik sekocinya.
Brengsek.</font>

446
00:32:11,109 --> 00:32:12,209
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya.</font>

447
00:32:12,609 --> 00:32:14,509
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau dari Kantor Kejaksaan Agung.</font>

448
00:32:15,379 --> 00:32:16,479
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada apa kemari?</font>

449
00:32:21,209 --> 00:32:24,309
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau dan aku sibuk dengan
