450
00:32:24,309 --> 00:32:26,709
<font color=#FFFF00>Jadi kupersingkat saja.</font>

451
00:32:28,509 --> 00:32:29,609
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku...</font>

452
00:32:30,679 --> 00:32:32,609
<font color=#FFFF00>...kakaknya Yoon So Hee.</font>

453
00:32:34,179 --> 00:32:36,979
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau tahu siapa Yoon So Hee?</font>

454
00:32:36,979 --> 00:32:40,249
<font color=#FFFF00>Tentu saja. Aku
