455
00:32:41,279 --> 00:32:42,609
<font color=#FFFF00>Kemarin...,</font>

456
00:32:43,749 --> 00:32:46,949
<font color=#FFFF00>...aku menerima laporan bahwa
mayatnya ditemukan di Cina.</font>

457
00:32:48,249 --> 00:32:50,309
<font color=#FFFF00>Sungguh disayangkan.</font>

458
00:32:51,509 --> 00:32:54,149
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tahu ucapanmu
