467
00:33:22,209 --> 00:33:24,849
<font color=#FFFF00>Berapa banyak yang kau tahu?</font>

468
00:33:29,409 --> 00:33:30,909
<font color=#FFFF00><i>[Putar Rekaman]</i></font>

469
00:33:32,049 --> 00:33:34,679
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku membunuhnya.</i></font>

470
00:33:36,709 --> 00:33:38,909
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku membunuh Yoon So Hee.</i></font>

471
00:33:39,909 --> 00:33:41,049
<font color=#FFFF00>Sebanyak inilah yang kutahu.</font>

472
00:33:44,779 --> 00:33:47,909
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku pun juga cuma
