473
00:33:49,809 --> 00:33:51,649
<font color=#FFFF00>Darimana kau dapat rekaman itu?</font>

474
00:33:51,749 --> 00:33:54,049
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tidak bisa menyembunyikan
kebenaran selamanya.</font>

475
00:33:55,179 --> 00:33:57,379
<font color=#FFFF00>Seberapa besar usahamu pun...,</font>

476
00:33:57,949 --> 00:34:00,749
<font color=#FFFF00>...kebenaran pasti
