477
00:34:01,409 --> 00:34:02,879
<font color=#FFFF00>Itulah sifat
dasar suatu kebenaran.</font>

478
00:34:02,879 --> 00:34:05,209
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tahu darimana kalau
