518
00:36:30,779 --> 00:36:33,079
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku hidup dari ajaranmu.</font>

519
00:36:33,379 --> 00:36:36,079
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku hidup menurut jaksa
senior yang hebat sepertimu.</font>

520
00:36:42,309 --> 00:36:43,579
<font color=#FFFF00>Kuharap...</font>

521
00:36:43,979 --> 00:36:46,619
<font color=#FFFF00>...kau akan melakukan seperti
